title: Welcome!
text:
Welcome!

Hi, I’m Johann! 🖐

Nice to meet you! 😊
I’m an economic/data analyst at the Department of Education (Australian Government). I completed my Bachelor of Economics minoring in Econometrics and Bachelor of Science majoring in Quantitative Environmental Modelling and minoring in Applied Statistics from the Australian National University in 2023. You can access my CV here.

Passion

Data Analysis
Data Visualisation
Public Health Data
Environmental Data



Extra-Curricalar

Co-Chair Data Analyst Network 2024
